---
// Hero.astro
---
<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 via-blue-800 to-blue-900 py-16 md:py-24 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Adorno decorativo de fondo -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-20 -mr-20 opacity-20">
    <svg width="400" height="400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="text-white">
        <path d="M20 16V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v9m16 0H4m16 0a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1a2 2 0 0 1 2-2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center md:text-left grid md:grid-cols-2 items-center gap-12">
    <div>
      <span class="inline-block bg-orange-500 text-white text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6 shadow-lg">
        Actualizado 2026
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Encuentra la laptop <span class="text-blue-400">perfecta</span> para tu presupuesto
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-blue-100 mb-8 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
        Analizamos y filtramos las mejores ofertas de Amazon para que no pierdas tiempo. Potencia, portabilidad y precio en un solo lugar.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
        <a href="#catalogo" class="bg-white text-blue-900 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-orange-500 hover:text-white transition-all shadow-xl transform active:scale-95 text-center">
          Ver Catalogo
        </a>
        <a href="/productos/2" class="border-2 border-blue-400 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-400/10 transition-all text-center">
          Oferta Destacada
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Imagen o Icono representativo -->
    <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center items-center">
      <div class="relative">
         <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-400 blur-3xl opacity-20 rounded-full"></div>
         <img 
  src="/hero-laptop.png" 
  alt="Laptop Destacada" 
  class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[210px] h-auto drop-shadow-2xl rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-700"
   
/>


      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
